lead_paragraph: Andy Murray's climb to the top of the world rankings took a while longer than it takes thrill-seeking tourists to reach the summit of the O2 Arena roof walk. Ten years in fact.

headline.print_headline: Back to Business for Murray as He Aims to End Year on High
